headline: Here's Why You Should Retain Cencora Stock in Your Portfolio Now
summary: Cencora's strength in U.S. Healthcare Solutions, along with rising specialty drug demand and biosimilar adoption, supports growth, though competitive pressures and international weakness remain headwinds.
